   <conbody>
      <p class="- topic/p ">Exclusion of the products is enabled for all qualification and product rows that are listed either for product categories or for custom product groups. You can exclude certain products under the selected category which are being qualified or benefited.</p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">
         <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Exclude() </b>hyperlink is available on every product (except type as product group and product) row with a number included in the bracket which indicates any product exclusions are made and saved.</p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">On clicking <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Exclude</b>, a new dialog box appears as shown in the following figure. You can select products assigned at different nodes of the product category for exclusion.</p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">
         <fig class="- topic/fig ">
            <image height="250"
                   placement="break"
