                   href="../attachments/102432707/107118629.png"
                   class="- topic/image "/>
         </fig>
      </p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">
         <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Deleting Products</b>
      </p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">You can delete the product rows for Reward Saving Program only in <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Draft</b> or <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">In Amendment</b> statuses. You can also delete the qualification and benefits products by selecting the product row and clicking on the section level <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Delete</b> button on the page.</p>
